            "text": "{\"code\":200,\"msg\":\"success\",\"data\":{\"taskId\":\"98df596956d0513544e2085da763c46c\",\"param\":\"Pop, Mysterious\",\"result\":\"Mysterious pop built around a hushed intro with sparse felt piano, breathy synth pads, and close-miked vocal lines in lots of space. The quietest sections carry the heaviest bar: a sudden drop to sub-heavy 808 kick, distorted tom hits, punchy snare, and low brass stabs. Wide chorus, delay throws, and tense minor-key hooks.\",\"creditsConsumed\":0.4,\"creditsRemaining\":29212.53,\"successFlag\":\"成功\",\"errorCode\":null,\"errorMsg\":null,\"createTime\":1777379281542}}"
